<paragraph id="93683FDA1F6D347B5DB73DDFA729A876" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
<taxonomicName id="66C788C6FCBDDCCFAD084C5B2418AB16" authority="Hull" authorityName="Hull" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Myiacerapis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Myiacerapis" order="Diptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Myiacerapis</taxonomicName>
Hull, 1949: 309. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="825B61BEE6B9D85AEF52AB17A9FCFB23" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Microdon" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Microdon villosus" order="Diptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="villosus">Microdon villosus</taxonomicName>
